class Solution:
    def maxChunksToSorted(self, arr: List[int]) -> int:
        n = len(arr)
        stack = []
        
        for i in range(n):
            while stack and arr[i] > arr[stack[-1]]:
                top = stack.pop()
                arr[top], arr[i] = arr[i], arr[top]
            
            stack.append(i)
        
        return len(stack)
